# Test context

Editing tests. See docs/CODING_STANDARDS.md §13, §17

## Quick checks

- Mock `next/image`, IntersectionObserver, fetch
- Prefer `getByRole`, `getByLabelText` over `getByTestId`
- Test behavior and outcomes, not implementation
- One concern per test when possible
